{"title":"亚运赛场采光（组诗）","authors":["白金"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":9,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚运赛场采光（组诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写在工人体育场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲的意志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从四面八方走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来这里高举圣火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赛出满天霞彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超常的真实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永久的缅怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成熟的青春在飞跃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸽哨中百花盛开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写在地坛体育馆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力，从地心拔起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直上浩茫的天宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亘古以来，砌筑长城的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是赫然的躯体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果杠铃上铸有命运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么都请来挺胸一举"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城会调动三山五岳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给你擎天的欢喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写在光彩体育馆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万个体劳动者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捐赠了这座光彩大厦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在亚洲体育史上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"植出一片光彩的绿洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光，吸满绿洲的温柔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地，荡漾阳光的淳厚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竞争和拚搏都是和谐的变奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟声正叩响可爱的金秋"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}